4
00:00:51,937 --> 00:00:54,092
Monk Myung Chul!

5
00:00:58,768 --> 00:01:00,440
Bong Pal!

6
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:26,048
Bong Pal, are you okay?

7
00:01:26,050 --> 00:01:28,038
Monk Myung Chul.

8
00:01:29,059 --> 00:01:30,815
Monk Myung Chul.

9
00:01:30,816 --> 00:01:32,651
Monk Myung Chul!

10
00:01:32,652 --> 00:01:36,783
Monk Myung Chul! Wake up!
Monk Myung Chul!

11
00:01:56,778 --> 00:01:59,206
Bong Pal.

12
00:01:59,207 --> 00:02:01,493
- Bong Pal.
- Monk Myung Chul.

13
00:02:03,366 --> 00:02:06,554
Move your hand, punk.
I can't breathe.

14
00:02:07,685 --> 00:02:09,401
Are you okay?

15
00:02:14,249 --> 00:02:16,352
Help me up.

16
00:02:27,816 --> 00:02:30,463
Let's see that punk.

17
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:45,481
Goodness, this rascal.
The gods have looked kindly upon him.

18
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:49,791
He's still breathing.

19
00:02:49,792 --> 00:02:53,563
Goodness, you suffered a lot too.

20
00:02:53,564 --> 00:02:57,362
You went through a lot.

21
00:03:02,625 --> 00:03:05,195
Bong Pal! Hyun Ji!

22
00:03:28,958 --> 00:03:30,988
<i>[Final Episode]</i>

23
00:03:31,408 --> 00:03:33,058
Good job.

24
00:03:58,904 --> 00:04:02,423
Let's go, Mr. Joo Hye Sung. Let's go.

25
00:04:27,832 --> 00:04:29,421
Monk.

26
00:04:30,582 --> 00:04:32,853
What is going to happen to
Professor Joo Hye Sung now?

27
00:04:32,854 --> 00:04:36,594
In some ways, he's a victim too.

28
00:04:37,293 --> 00:04:41,916
In our eyes, yes. But to normal
people, he is just a murderer.

29
00:04:42,433 --> 00:04:47,017
An evil spirit took over his body because
he had hatred in his heart at the start.

30
00:04:47,019 --> 00:04:51,010
You can't overlook that crime.

31
00:04:52,053 --> 00:04:54,460
Oh dear Buddha.

32
00:05:03,188 --> 00:05:07,832
I'm going to go home and get some rest.
You take Hyun Ji home.

33
00:05:07,834 --> 00:05:09,455
Yes.

34
00:05:09,457 --> 00:05:12,308
I'll see you later.

35
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,334
Hyun Ji!

36
00:05:36,412 --> 00:05:39,249
Let me look at you! Are you okay?

37
00:05:39,250 --> 00:05:41,031
You're not hurt anywhere?

38
00:05:41,686 --> 00:05:43,282
I'm okay.

39
00:05:46,096 --> 00:05:49,142
- Dad.
- Let's go inside.

40
00:05:49,144 --> 00:05:54,903
Young man, I clearly told you that
I do not like you seeing Hyun Ji.

41
00:05:54,904 --> 00:05:57,253
She's been in danger twice
already because of you.

42
00:05:58,159 --> 00:06:00,813
- What if she got hurt?
- I'm sorry.

43
00:06:01,462 --> 00:06:04,101
Mom, stop. Bong Pal did nothing wrong.

44
00:06:04,103 --> 00:06:07,517
Go inside the house with your dad.
Take her inside.

45
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:10,236
- Mom.
- Honey.

46
00:06:11,005 --> 00:06:13,015
Let's go, Hyun Ji.

47
00:06:24,796 --> 00:06:28,733
We're going to leave here tomorrow.

48
00:06:28,734 --> 00:06:32,194
If you have feelings for
Hyun Ji, then end it here.

49
00:06:32,195 --> 00:06:34,856
It's best for both of you.

50
00:06:35,353 --> 00:06:38,301
I believe you understand me.

51
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:42,287
Ma'am.

52
00:06:50,702 --> 00:06:54,193
Please give this to Hyun Ji.

53
00:06:58,693 --> 00:07:00,921
Please.

54
00:07:17,332 --> 00:07:19,015
No Hyun Joo.

55
00:07:20,935 --> 00:07:22,928
Im Hyun Soo.

56
00:07:23,940 --> 00:07:25,592
Park Ji Hoon.

57
00:07:33,274 --> 00:07:35,763
And Joo Jin Myung.

58
00:07:39,719 --> 00:07:41,899
You remember these people, right?

59
00:07:45,022 --> 00:07:47,233
Mr. Joo Hye Sung.

60
00:07:58,517 --> 00:08:00,323
Yes.

61
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:05,854
I remember.

62
00:08:30,206 --> 00:08:32,666
I killed them.

63
00:08:38,657 --> 00:08:40,623
I...

64
00:08:45,290 --> 00:08:48,253
killed all these people.

65
00:09:08,331 --> 00:09:10,253
Hye Sung.

66
00:09:25,343 --> 00:09:27,067
Hye Sung.

67
00:09:58,886 --> 00:10:01,809
- You're home.
- Yes.

68
00:10:06,854 --> 00:10:08,979
Is it okay to drink when you're injured?

69
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:12,911
There's no medicine for
getting beaten by a ghost.

70
00:10:12,912 --> 00:10:15,734
Alcohol is the best
to overcome the pain.

71
00:10:17,075 --> 00:10:18,807
There's no food either.

72
00:10:18,809 --> 00:10:20,748
Just wait a little bit.

73
00:10:24,814 --> 00:10:26,623
Thanks.

74
00:10:28,642 --> 00:10:31,600
Gosh, this looks good.

75
00:10:35,633 --> 00:10:40,042
Wow, you really know how to cook.

76
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,746
Is Hyun Ji leaving?

77
00:10:45,498 --> 00:10:48,146
Yes, she's leaving tomorrow.

78
00:10:48,147 --> 00:10:51,440
I see. It's time for everyone
to go back to their normal lives.

79
00:10:52,431 --> 00:10:54,324
You must be sad.

80
00:10:54,325 --> 00:10:57,051
- No, I'm fine.
- Good.

81
00:10:57,052 --> 00:11:01,175
It's not like distance is going
to break you two apart, right?

82
00:11:01,176 --> 00:11:04,330
On days like this,
let's drink up and go to bed.

83
00:11:07,498 --> 00:11:10,003
Oh goodness.

84
00:11:16,536 --> 00:11:18,162
This is nice.

85
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:30,878
Why did you do it? I know it wasn't you.

86
00:11:31,416 --> 00:11:35,036
- Let's talk to the detective again...
- I did it.

87
00:11:37,297 --> 00:11:42,232
The crimes I committed in my heart are
bigger than the ones I physically did.

88
00:11:44,863 --> 00:11:47,816
If I didn't have those bad
intentions in my heart back then...

89
00:11:49,282 --> 00:11:51,849
It wouldn't have come to be like this.

90
00:11:56,571 --> 00:11:58,466
My hand...

91
00:11:59,949 --> 00:12:02,959
I killed those people in my heart.

92
00:12:04,445 --> 00:12:06,835
That fact will never change.

93
00:12:06,836 --> 00:12:08,761
- Hye Sung.
- And...

94
00:12:10,091 --> 00:12:13,363
don't ever come here
again. If you see my face...

95
00:12:14,628 --> 00:12:17,247
It will only give you pain.

96
00:12:21,891 --> 00:12:24,291
No, it's not true.

97
00:12:24,865 --> 00:12:26,963
I'm going to come every day.

98
00:12:26,964 --> 00:12:29,612
I'm going to come and see you.

99
00:12:29,613 --> 00:12:32,759
I'm going to keep coming
until you forgive me.

100
00:12:32,761 --> 00:12:36,021
I'm going to come even
if you refuse to see me.

101
00:12:36,022 --> 00:12:39,932
I'm going to come every day to see you.

102
00:13:17,458 --> 00:13:20,088
- What's Hyun Ji doing?
- She's talking in her room.

103
00:13:20,089 --> 00:13:21,713
With who?

104
00:13:21,714 --> 00:13:25,762
- I swear.
- Leave her alone. It's the last time.

105
00:13:33,793 --> 00:13:36,194
I'm leaving today.

106
00:13:36,195 --> 00:13:38,554
Our stuff is all packed and ready to go.

107
00:13:41,449 --> 00:13:43,355
Bong Pal.

108
00:13:43,901 --> 00:13:46,737
I hope you understand why Mom did that.

109
00:13:46,738 --> 00:13:48,449
<i>I completely understand.</i>

110
00:13:48,450 --> 00:13:50,672
<i>Don't worry about it.</i>

111
00:13:50,674 --> 00:13:54,184
- Thanks.
- <i>Study hard down there.</i>

112
00:13:54,185 --> 00:13:59,606
- <i>That way we'll be able to meet quickly.</i>
- I will.

113
00:13:59,607 --> 00:14:01,917
<i>Hyun Ji, let's go.</i>

114
00:14:02,647 --> 00:14:04,570
I have to go now.

115
00:14:43,575 --> 00:14:46,042
Hyun Ji, get in.

116
00:14:46,739 --> 00:14:47,839
Okay.

117
00:15:22,498 --> 00:15:24,631
<i>I don't want to go.</i>

118
00:15:24,632 --> 00:15:27,208
<i>I want to be with you.</i>

119
00:15:27,209 --> 00:15:29,487
I don't want to send you off either.

120
00:15:29,488 --> 00:15:31,523
Why aren't you here to see me?

121
00:15:31,525 --> 00:15:34,583
I don't know when we'll
see each other again.

122
00:15:36,094 --> 00:15:39,127
- Don't you miss me?
- I do miss you.

123
00:15:40,792 --> 00:15:46,681
But I'm afraid I won't be able
to let you go if I see you.

124
00:15:47,812 --> 00:15:49,892
- Bong Pal.
- <i>Hyun Ji.</i>

125
00:15:49,893 --> 00:15:55,249
<i>I want you to get back to your
normal life as soon as possible.</i>

126
00:15:56,103 --> 00:15:59,017
I don't want you to put
anything off because of me.

127
00:15:59,018 --> 00:16:04,948
<i>We'll be apart for now, but we can always
be together once you come to college.</i>

128
00:16:04,949 --> 00:16:10,778
Once that happens, let's formally ask
for your mother's permission to date.

129
00:16:13,526 --> 00:16:18,310
I know it'll be hard...
but let's look forward to that day.

130
00:16:18,311 --> 00:16:20,498
<i>Let's be patient and wait.</i>

131
00:16:20,499 --> 00:16:23,271
Okay, I will.

132
00:16:26,004 --> 00:16:28,943
Take care of yourself until then.

133
00:16:55,659 --> 00:16:58,473
This is how you're supposed
to eat a lettuce wrap.

134
00:17:13,142 --> 00:17:14,567
Where's my phone?

135
00:17:15,939 --> 00:17:17,604
Hello?

136
00:17:18,664 --> 00:17:23,643
Yes, this is the 24-hour exorcism
service, how may I help you?

137
00:17:32,866 --> 00:17:39,569
Chapter eight on conjunction.
Please turn to the correct page.

138
