are waiting to be rescued?

723
00:59:34,578 --> 00:59:36,187
Hold on.

724
00:59:40,198 --> 00:59:43,606
Hello, this is 24-hour
exorcism service, Sundae Soup.

725
00:59:43,607 --> 00:59:48,277
