and sadness just like us.

747
01:01:29,678 --> 01:01:32,868
My son. My son.

748
01:02:03,417 --> 01:02:05,737
- Monk Myung Chul.
- Yes?

749
01:02:05,738 --> 01:02:09,427
Why do you exorcise?

750
01:02:09,428 --> 01:02:12,277
It's a tough job, but doesn't pay much.

751
01:02:16,008 --> 01:02:19,316
I help with the lingering attachment
of the ghosts who can't leave yet.

752
01:02:19,317 --> 01:02:22,436
I help get rid of people's fear.

753
01:02:22,437 --> 01:02:26,487
That way, everybody finds their way back.

754
01:02:26,488 --> 01:02:28,487
They go back to the places
where they belong.

755
01:02:28,488 --> 01:02:29,916
That's why I do it.

756
01:02:29,917 --> 01:02:34,107
Do you think I can do the job?

757
01:02:36,308 --> 01:02:38,178
Bong Pal.

758
01:02:39,317 --> 01:02:41,296
When I found out that
you'd go around exorcising

759
01:02:41,297 --> 01:02:43,598
do you know why I was so against that?

760
01:02:45,357 --> 01:02:46,657
Not sure.

761
01:02:46,658 --> 01:02:49,896
It was because I could see
hatred in your eyes then.

762
01:02:49,897 --> 01:02:52,936
You can't see the world right
when you have so much anger in you.

763
01:02:52,937 --> 01:02:54,936
You were hurt by ghosts.

764
01:02:54,937 --> 01:02:57,287
But not all ghosts are bad.

765
01:02:57,288 --> 01:03:00,206
In a way, we should feel sorry for them.

766
01:03:00,207 --> 01:03:02,957
Are you asking if you can do the job?

767
01:03:03,328 --> 01:03:05,997
It's up to you what you think.

768
01:03:06,348 --> 01:03:12,007
Making others happy makes you happiest.

769
01:03:12,008 --> 01:03:14,407
If your eyes can give the dead ones peace

770
01:03:14,408 --> 01:03:18,607
you're not cursed,
but you have a special gift.

771
01:03:23,377 --> 01:03:27,126
By the way, it's so unlike you
that you're saying all good things.

772
01:03:27,127 --> 01:03:29,607
When do I ever say bad things, punk?

773
01:03:30,178 --> 01:03:32,767
- I think this is your first time.
- What?

774
01:03:32,768 --> 01:03:35,417
Please continue.

775
01:03:37,817 --> 01:03:40,467
Ah, it's so good.

776
01:03:40,468 --> 01:03:43,547
- This is really nice.
- Yes.

777
01:03:44,268 --> 01:03:46,177
How long has it been?

778
01:03:46,178 --> 01:03:49,336
Seriously, how long has it been?

779
01:03:49,337 --> 01:03:52,928
I love going together like this!

780
01:03:54,457 --> 01:03:56,607
Hyun Ji. Bong Pal.

781
01:03:57,268 --> 01:03:59,396
Let's do this for the rest of our lives!

782
01:03:59,397 --> 01:04:01,227
Do this forever!

783
01:04:03,187 --> 01:04:05,227
Let's go!

784
01:04:40,078 --> 01:04:41,797
Bong Pal.

785
01:04:42,788 --> 01:04:44,317
Yes?

786
01:04:44,747 --> 01:04:47,288
Why did you change your mind so suddenly?

787
01:04:49,268 --> 01:04:51,496
- I want to know.
- Know what?

788
01:04:51,497 --> 01:04:54,008
The reason why we can see ghosts.

789
01:04:56,357 --> 01:04:57,997
Let's go.

790
01:05:04,797 --> 01:05:08,997
- Let's fight ghosts!
- Let's fight ghosts!

791
01:05:28,973 --> 01:05:30,973
<i>[Let’s Fight Ghost]</i>

